{"questionId":"22579565","questionHtml":"<p>Find the coordinates of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">B</mi></math>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>valid attempt to find <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math>-coordinates (e.g. solving <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>12</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>18</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math> or graphing <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></math>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>point <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">B</mi></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>point <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>5625</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo> </mo><mfenced><mrow><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>563</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced>